value.excerpt: Former President Donald Trump is "really concerned" about the migrant situation along the U.S.-Mexico border and may schedule a visit to the region, a former Trump aide said this week.

value.title: Romney receives JFK 'Profile in Courage' award for voting to convict Trump on first impeachment charge
